channel.title: This message shows up when I try to run my server!
channel.description:
This message shows up when I try to run my server: [code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 16 at ItemHandler.loadItemList(ItemHandler.java:283) at ItemHandler.<init>(ItemHandler.java:173) at server.main(server.java:111)[/code]
I cannot log onto my server. I have heard that it has something to do with my Item.Java, but I checked the items I modified, and they are fine. Please tell me how to fix this! Thanks!
~Jc22493
